column2: select p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, s.z as redshift from galaxy p, specobj s, dbo.fgetNearByObjEq (#, #, #) n where p.objid = s.bestobjid and p.objid = n.objid and s.bestobjid = n.objid and (p.g BETWEEN # AND #) and (p.r BETWEEN # AND #) and (p.i BETWEEN # AND #) and s.z BETWEEN # AND #
